    "we write $\\mathbf{x} \\in \\mathbb{R}^n$.\n",
    "Formally, we call $n$ the *dimensionality* of the vector.\n",
    "[**In code, this corresponds to the tensor's length**],\n",
    "accessible via Python's built-in `len` function.\n"
   ]
